label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":39,"end":49,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":91,"end":92,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎（Infectious bronchitis，简称：IB）是由鸡传染性支气管炎病毒（Infectious bronchitis virus，简称：IBV）引起、发生在鸡身上的一种病害。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"食欲降低","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"体温升高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"张口呼吸","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"流鼻液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"鼻液","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡食欲降低，体温升高，张口呼吸，咳嗽、流鼻液。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":19,"text":"高度传染性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":28,"text":"病毒性呼吸道疾病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎是一种急性、高度传染性的病毒性呼吸道疾病。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"种鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"生长性能下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"死淘率升高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":32,"text":"产蛋量及蛋壳质量下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 常导致蛋鸡、种鸡的生长性能下降、死淘率升高、产蛋量及蛋壳质量下降，造成严重的经济损失，是养鸡业的重要疫病之一。

label: [{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"隔离","labels":["control"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"检疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"注意通风","labels":["control"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"饲养密度","labels":["control"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"保温","labels":["control"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"疫苗免疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 该病害以预防为主。严格执行隔离、检疫、消毒等卫生防疫措施,加强饲养管理,注意通风、饲养密度、保温等管理措施，最主要的是做好疫苗免疫工作。

label: [{"start":4,"end":10,"text":"病鸡气管嘤音","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"伸脖呼吸","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"眼湿润","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"流鼻液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":39,"end":46,"text":"大于6周龄的鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":16,"text":"脖","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"鼻液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":31,"text":"眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"鼻液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"嘤音","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"湿润","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 呼吸型：病鸡气管嘤音、咳嗽和伸脖呼吸，夜间寂静时较明显，病鸡眼湿润，流鼻液，但大于6周龄的鸡常无鼻液；

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"气管环黏膜充血潮红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"脓性分泌物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"气管环黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"潮红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"细支气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 气管环黏膜充血潮红，气管、支气管、细支气管都有脓性分泌物；其他脏器无明显症状。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"育雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"健康鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"鸡冠发红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":59,"text":"腹部肿胀下垂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"肿胀下垂","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"发红","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"鸡冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 生殖型：育雏早期感染IBV后，临床上发病不明显，死亡率也很低。然而到成年时，外观看似健康鸡，鸡冠发红，有的腹部肿胀下垂。

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":20,"text":"输卵管有透明液体渗出物","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":28,"text":"输卵管堵塞","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":44,"text":"可见输卵管前端萎缩或发育不全","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"前端萎缩","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"发育不全","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":67,"text":"成熟卵泡无法进入输卵管形成蛋坠落到腹腔中","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":70,"end":77,"text":"产蛋障碍综合征","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":20,"text":"透明液体渗出物","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"堵塞","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"成熟卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":58,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":84,"end":86,"text":"母鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 剖检卵巢发育正常，输卵管有透明液体渗出物，导致输卵管堵塞，还可见输卵管前端萎缩或发育不全，导致成熟卵泡无法进入输卵管形成蛋坠落到腹腔中，造成产蛋障碍综合征，即所谓的“假母鸡”。

label: [{"start":8,"end":15,"text":"轻微呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"羽毛逆立","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":50,"end":54,"text":"鸡爪干枯","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":55,"end":61,"text":"机体脱水严重","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":62,"end":65,"text":"肾肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"逆立","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"干枯","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"鸡爪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":63,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"精神沉","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":49,"text":"排米汤样白色粪便","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"肾型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 肾型：发病初期有轻微呼吸道症状，随后呼吸道症状消失，但随后病鸡表现羽毛逆立，精神沉排米汤样白色粪便，鸡爪干枯；机体脱水严重，肾肿大、苍白；

label: [{"start":0,"end":12,"text":"肾小管和输尿管充满尿酸郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"输尿管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"肾小管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":25,"text":"泄殖腔中有白色尿酸盐","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"泄殖腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":44,"text":"两侧输尿管因尿酸盐沉积而明显扩张变粗","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"扩张变粗","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"两侧输尿管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 肾小管和输尿管充满尿酸郁，盐，泄殖腔中有白色尿酸盐，两侧输尿管因尿酸盐沉积而明显扩张变粗。

label: [{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"病鸡消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"拉稀","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"死亡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":33,"text":"腺胃肿大呈球状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":39,"text":"腺冒壁增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":46,"text":"腺胃乳头溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":65,"end":68,"text":"蛋重轻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":69,"end":72,"text":"体型小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":73,"end":79,"text":"腺胃乳头明显","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"呈球状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"腺冒壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":44,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":73,"end":77,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"腺胃型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 腺胃型：病鸡消瘦，有的有呼吸道症状，拉稀，出现死亡；腺胃肿大呈球状，腺冒壁增厚，腺胃乳头溃疡；100日龄前可见明显病变；产蛋后仅见蛋重轻、体型小、腺胃乳头明显。

label: [{"start":5,"end":19,"text":"病鸡深部胸肌组织呈胶冻样水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":28,"text":"洞体表现湿润外观","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"肠炎症","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":38,"text":"气管黏膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"胶冻样","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"胸肌组织","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"洞体","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"气管黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"湿润外观","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"肾型变异","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 肾型变异：病鸡深部胸肌组织呈胶冻样水肿，洞体表现湿润外观:卵巢、气管黏膜充血；出现肠炎症。

label: [{"start":2,"end":10,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":21,"text":"发病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 根据鸡传染性支气管炎的流行情况，结合发病鸡的临床症状和剖检变化，即可做出初步诊断；如需要进一步确诊，需要进行病毒的分离和鉴定等实验室技术来确诊。

label: [{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"检疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"隔离","labels":["control"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"通风","labels":["control"]},{"start":51,"end":55,"text":"饲养密度","labels":["control"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"保温","labels":["control"]},{"start":71,"end":75,"text":"疫苗免疫","labels":["control"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":5,"end":13,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 预防措施：鸡传染性支气管炎以预防为主，严格执行隔离、检疫、消毒等卫生防疫措施，加强饲养管理，注意通风、饲养密度、保温等管理措施，最主要的是做好疫苗免疫工作。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"改善饲养管理条件","labels":["control"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"降低饲养密度","labels":["control"]},{"start":35,"end":41,"text":"注意温度变化","labels":["control"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"避免过冷","labels":["control"]},{"start":67,"end":77,"text":"温度变化幅度不能过大","labels":["control"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":23,"text":"加强内空气流通","labels":["control"]},{"start":47,"end":55,"text":"过热保证室内温度","labels":["control"]}]
text: 改善饲养管理条件，降低饲养密度，加强内空气流通防止有害气体刺激呼吸道，注意温度变化，避免过冷、过热保证室内温度在26~28°C，密度、温度变化幅度不能过大。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"科学配合饲料","labels":["control"]},{"start":7,"end":15,"text":"蛋白含量不能过高","labels":["control"]},{"start":17,"end":25,"text":"减轻肾脏代谢负担","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":33,"text":"补充多种维生素","labels":["control"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":33,"text":"维生素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"维生素A","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 科学配合饲料，蛋白含量不能过高。以减轻肾脏代谢负担，补充多种维生素，尤其是维生素A，以增强机体的抵抗力。

label: [{"start":5,"end":13,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":29,"text":"利用中药抗病毒药物降低病毒的危害","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"中药抗病毒药物","labels":["drug"]},{"start":65,"end":69,"text":"加强通风","labels":["control"]},{"start":70,"end":81,"text":"增加多种维生素的供应量","labels":["control"]},{"start":34,"end":44,"text":"在饮水中添加消肿利尿","labels":["control"]},{"start":45,"end":52,"text":"促进排除尿酸盐","labels":["control"]},{"start":53,"end":64,"text":"调节体内酸碱平衡的药物","labels":["control"]},{"start":53,"end":64,"text":"调节体内酸碱平衡的药物","labels":["drug"]},{"start":74,"end":77,"text":"维生素","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 治疗措施：鸡传染性支气管炎利用中药抗病毒药物降低病毒的危害。同时可以在饮水中添加消肿利尿、促进排除尿酸盐、调节体内酸碱平衡的药物。加强通风，增加多种维生素的供应量。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"中药组方","labels":["drug"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"板蓝根","labels":["drug"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"大青叶","labels":["drug"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"鱼腥草","labels":["drug"]},{"start":32,"end":35,"text":"穿心莲","labels":["drug"]},{"start":40,"end":41,"text":"黄","labels":["drug"]},{"start":46,"end":49,"text":"蒲公英","labels":["drug"]},{"start":54,"end":57,"text":"金银花","labels":["drug"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"地榆","labels":["drug"]},{"start":69,"end":71,"text":"薄荷","labels":["drug"]},{"start":75,"end":77,"text":"甘草","labels":["drug"]},{"start":88,"end":89,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":110,"end":112,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":115,"end":117,"text":"半夏","labels":["drug"]},{"start":121,"end":124,"text":"桑白皮","labels":["drug"]},{"start":129,"end":131,"text":"桔梗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":95,"end":108,"text":"水煎服或开水浸泡后拌料饲喂","labels":["control"]}]
text: 常用的中药组方：板蓝根250g、大青叶100g、鱼腥草250g、穿心莲200g、黄250g、蒲公英250g、金银花250g、地榆100g、薄荷50g、甘草50g（此为1000只鸡1天用量），水煎服或开水浸泡后拌料饲喂，若咳嗽，则加半夏50g、桑白皮100g、桔梗100g。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"板蓝根","labels":["drug"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"连翘","labels":["drug"]},{"start":9,"end":12,"text":"金银花","labels":["drug"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"陈皮","labels":["drug"]},{"start":16,"end":17,"text":"黄","labels":["drug"]},{"start":44,"end":53,"text":"在饮水中加入多维素","labels":["control"]},{"start":50,"end":53,"text":"多维素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":31,"end":35,"text":"拌入饲料","labels":["control"]}]
text: 或取板蓝根、连翘、金银花、陈皮、黄各等份，研细后按0.3%的量拌入饲料中，连用3天，同时在饮水中加入多维素，一般在3天后疫情可得到控制。

label: [{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"鸡传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"泌尿生殖道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":51,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":56,"text":"神经系统","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":24,"text":"冠状病毒属传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"高度接触性","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 鸡传染性支气管炎是由冠状病毒属传染性支气管炎病毒引起鸡的一种急性、高度接触性呼吸道、泌尿生殖道、消化道和神经系统疾病。

label: [{"start":5,"end":20,"text":"冠状病毒属鸡传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":35,"text":"呼吸道分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":36,"end":37,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":39,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":40,"end":41,"text":"脾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"血液","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":48,"text":"腔上囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 本病病原为冠状病毒属鸡传染性支气管炎病毒，主要存在于病鸡的呼吸道分泌物、肾、肝、脾、血液、腔上囊等。

label: [{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"酒精","labels":["drug"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"乙醚","labels":["drug"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"氯仿","labels":["drug"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"胆盐","labels":["drug"]},{"start":39,"end":42,"text":"来苏儿","labels":["drug"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"高锰酸钾","labels":["drug"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"酒精","labels":["drug"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"福尔马林","labels":["drug"]},{"start":27,"end":32,"text":"一般消毒药","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 本病毒耐酸碱，不耐热，对酒精、乙醚、氯仿、胆盐敏感，对一般消毒药均敏感，如1%来苏儿、0.01%高锰酸钾、70%酒精、1%福尔马林，数分钟即可灭活。

label: [{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"呼吸道血清型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":51,"end":57,"text":"肾病变血清型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"肠型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 本病毒血清型较复杂，现已分离出100多个株，已有30种血清型。现已知本病毒有11个呼吸道血清型，16个肾病变血清型，国外又分离出肠型。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"生殖道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":28,"text":"严重的肠道损伤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"损伤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"腹泻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":55,"text":"肌肉病变","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":56,"end":64,"text":"呼吸道病变不明显","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":56,"end":59,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":48,"end":49,"text":"腹","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 除可引发呼吸道、生殖道和肾病变外，还可造成严重的肠道损伤。还有产蛋鸡的变异毒株。英国又发现了引起腹泻和肌肉病变而呼吸道病变不明显的毒株。

label: [{"start":25,"end":35,"text":"喉和气管的组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":35,"text":"组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":26,"text":"喉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":58,"text":"明显的呼吸道症状及上呼吸道组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":53,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":58,"text":"组织学变化","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":85,"text":"明显呼吸道症状以及上呼吸道和支气管组织学病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":80,"end":85,"text":"组织学病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":65,"end":68,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":72,"end":76,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":77,"end":80,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":102,"end":107,"text":"间质性肾炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":92,"end":100,"text":"呼吸道症状与病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":92,"end":97,"text":"呼吸道症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":98,"end":100,"text":"病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":92,"end":95,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 我国分离出四个病理型：Ⅰ型不引起呼吸道症状，只引起喉和气管的组织学变化；Ⅱ型引起明显的呼吸道症状及上呼吸道组织学变化；Ⅲ型引起明显呼吸道症状以及上呼吸道和支气管组织学病变；Ⅳ型引起所有呼吸道症状与病变以及间质性肾炎。

label: [{"start":15,"end":24,"text":"传染性支气管炎病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 我国分离到的致腺胃病变的毒株是传染性支气管炎病毒快速变异的结果。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"青年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":16,"end":23,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":28,"end":37,"text":"变异传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":40,"end":49,"text":"肾型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":52,"end":62,"text":"腺胃型传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":50,"end":52,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 临床上常见的有引起雏鸡、青年鸡的传染性支气管炎、产蛋鸡的变异传染性支气管炎、幼鸡肾型传染性支气管炎、幼鸡腺胃型传染性支气管炎等。

label: [{"start":39,"end":46,"text":"传染性支气管炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":59,"end":81,"text":"临床取样分离毒株制备组织灭活苗或油乳剂灭活苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":65,"end":74,"text":"毒株制备组织灭活苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":75,"end":81,"text":"油乳剂灭活苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 本病毒还将会出现很多变异毒株，因此，免疫时用常规的疫苗很难奏效，这也是临床上对传染性支气管炎不易治愈的原因。所以，只有临床取样分离毒株制备组织灭活苗或油乳剂灭活苗才见实效。

label: [{"start":4,"end":5,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":21,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]}]
text: 仅发生于鸡，其他家禽均不感染，各种年龄的鸡均可发病，但以雏鸡较为严重。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"易感鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":63,"text":"易感鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":64,"end":66,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 主要通过呼吸道排除病毒，经空气、飞沫传给易感鸡，也可通过污染的蛋、饲料、饮水、用具等经消化道感染和垂直传染，传染性极强，易感鸡与病鸡同饲，可于48小时内出现症状。过热、严寒、拥挤、通风不良以及营养缺乏等饲养管理不当，均可促进本病的发生。四季均可发生，但以冬季最为严重。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":19,"text":"突然出现呼吸道症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"不见前驱症状","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病鸡常不见前驱症状，突然出现呼吸道症状，并迅速波及全群。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":4,"end":8,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"张口","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"喷嚏","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"咳嗽","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"喘息","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"气管啰音","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"流鼻涕","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":39,"text":"发出特殊叫声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":53,"text":"全身衰弱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":54,"end":58,"text":"食欲不振","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":63,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":64,"end":67,"text":"翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":49,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"伸颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"鼻涕","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":59,"end":61,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":64,"end":65,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":65,"end":67,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 病鸡表现精神沉郁、伸颈、张口、喷嚏、咳嗽、喘息、气管啰音和流鼻涕，发出特殊叫声。随着病情发展，病鸡全身衰弱，食欲不振，羽毛松乱，翅下垂。

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"鼻窦肿胀","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":16,"text":"流鼻涕","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"多眼泪","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"逐渐消瘦","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"产蛋率迅速下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"产软蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":42,"end":45,"text":"畸形蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"鼻窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"鼻涕","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"眼泪","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":29,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"肿胀","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":62,"text":"很难恢复到原来的产蛋率","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 2周龄以内的雏鸡鼻窦肿胀，流鼻涕，多眼泪，逐渐消瘦；成年鸡产蛋率迅速下降，并产软蛋、畸形蛋等，病愈后，很难恢复到原来的产蛋率。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"肾炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"肠炎","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"急性下痢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":40,"text":"上呼吸道症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":34,"end":38,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 感染侵害肾脏的毒株时，可引起肾炎、肠炎，并有急性下痢等，有的同时还有上呼吸道症状。

label: [{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"破坏卵巢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"停止发育","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":32,"text":"使母雏终身不产蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":36,"end":44,"text":"产蛋率下降或停产","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"母雏","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 感染侵害生殖系统的毒株时，可破坏卵巢，停止发育，使母雏终身不产蛋，成年鸡产蛋率下降或停产。

label: [{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 感染侵害神经系统的毒株时，可出现与鸡新城疫相似的神经症状。

label: [{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"支原体","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"大肠杆菌","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":27,"text":"6周龄以上的鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病程一般1～2周，雏鸡死亡率可达25%,6周龄以上的鸡死亡率低，若继发感染支原体、大肠杆菌时，则死亡率会很高。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"鼻腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"鼻窦","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"浆液性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":25,"text":"卡他性或干酪样渗出物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"气囊混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":31,"end":39,"text":"表面有黄色覆盖物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":51,"end":58,"text":"小面积的肺充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"气囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"混浊","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":43,"end":46,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 支气管、鼻腔、鼻窦中有浆液性、卡他性或干酪样渗出物，气囊混浊，表面有黄色覆盖物，在大的支气管周围，可见小面积的肺充血。

label: [{"start":0,"end":3,"text":"产蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"腹腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":6,"end":16,"text":"可见液体状的卵黄物质","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"卵泡出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"变形","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":41,"text":"输卵管发育异常","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"卵泡","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":41,"text":"发育异常","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 产蛋鸡腹腔内可见液体状的卵黄物质，卵泡出血、充血、变形；雏鸡有时可见输卵管发育异常。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"肾脏肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"花斑肾","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"肾小管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"扩张","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"增粗","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":64,"text":"直肠末端膨大充满大量石灰样稀便","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":71,"end":83,"text":"肝被膜有灰白色尿酸盐沉积","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":84,"end":89,"text":"喉头有黏液","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":93,"end":98,"text":"支气管充血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":100,"end":108,"text":"灰白色黏性分泌物","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":100,"end":103,"text":"灰白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":96,"end":98,"text":"充血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":75,"end":78,"text":"灰白色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":53,"text":"直肠末端","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":63,"end":64,"text":"便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":67,"end":70,"text":"心包膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":74,"text":"肝被膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":84,"end":86,"text":"喉头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":90,"end":92,"text":"气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":93,"end":96,"text":"支气管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":103,"end":108,"text":"黏性分泌物","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":59,"end":62,"text":"石灰样","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":26,"text":"肾","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":42,"text":"输尿管常充满尿酸盐结晶","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"输尿管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":87,"end":89,"text":"黏液","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 感染侵害肾脏的病毒株时，引起肾脏肿大、苍白，呈花斑肾，肾小管、输尿管常充满尿酸盐结晶，扩张，增粗，直肠末端膨大充满大量石灰样稀便；有的心包膜、肝被膜有灰白色尿酸盐沉积；喉头有黏液，气管、支气管充血，有灰白色黏性分泌物。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":25,"text":"腺胃极度肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":43,"text":"腺胃壁增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"黏膜水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":46,"end":48,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"增厚","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"极度肿胀","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":55,"end":65,"text":"腺胃乳头初期水肿发亮","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":61,"end":65,"text":"水肿发亮","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":75,"end":79,"text":"溃疡出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":68,"end":72,"text":"凹陷破溃","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":82,"end":93,"text":"腺胃乳头可挤出脓性液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":96,"end":108,"text":"腺胃乳头可见肉芽肿样病变","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":109,"end":113,"text":"个体变小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":114,"end":118,"text":"体重减轻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"腺胃","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":41,"text":"腺胃壁","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":44,"end":46,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":82,"end":86,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":96,"end":100,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":87,"end":93,"text":"挤出脓性液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":101,"end":108,"text":"见肉芽肿样病变","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 感染侵害腺胃的病毒株时，最明显的特征是腺胃极度肿胀，约为正常腺胃的2～5倍，腺胃壁增厚，黏膜水肿、充血、出血，腺胃乳头初期水肿发亮，中期凹陷破溃，后期溃疡出血，有时腺胃乳头可挤出脓性液体，有的腺胃乳头可见肉芽肿样病变。个体变小，体重减轻。

label: [{"start":4,"end":7,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":21,"text":"输卵管损害","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"损害","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":30,"text":"输卵管发育不全","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":37,"text":"失去产蛋能力","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"发育不全","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":52,"text":"产蛋期推迟","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"产异常蛋","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":58,"end":63,"text":"减产或停产","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":67,"end":74,"text":"输卵管发育不良","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":75,"end":77,"text":"短小","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":78,"end":82,"text":"管腔变细","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":83,"end":90,"text":"闭塞或形成囊泡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":92,"end":95,"text":"壁变薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":96,"end":102,"text":"内含透明液体","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":103,"end":109,"text":"呈球形或柱状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":67,"end":70,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":70,"end":74,"text":"发育不良","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":78,"end":80,"text":"管腔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 感染侵害输卵管的病毒株时，幼鸡的输卵管损害，使输卵管发育不全，失去产蛋能力；如开产前后感染，则产蛋期推迟，产异常蛋，减产或停产，剖检见输卵管发育不良，短小，管腔变细，闭塞或形成囊泡，其壁变薄，内含透明液体，呈球形或柱状。
